{"tid":1241002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持續抗爭係最難嘅野，但係呢個係成功嘅要點","createTime":"2019-06-18T14:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T14:39:09.000Z","uid":38966,"like":153,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a0a40cf530ea3db8b45493d5eb58c65333dfb4","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"民意好重要！<br />\n民意好重要！<br />\n民意好重要！<br />\n我有一個前提想睇大家係咪同意嘅<br />\n大家覺唔覺得林鄭道完歉之後，市民有軟化跡象？<br />\n雖然話遊行人數達到約200萬人，但係都有人係因為烈士而出黎，所以未必反映到不滿林鄭唔直接回應訴求嘅真實數字。<br />\n其實好大機會下次遊行人數就會開始下跌。<br />\n當軟化嘅市民見到政府有所謂嘅讓步，而我地依然咁激進架話，佢地可能會覺得我地唔理智，甚至係無理取鬧。<br />\n咁點樣先可以令我地嘅行為合理化呢？<br />\n我地要合理化到，即使軟化咗嘅市民都唔會有太大抗拒感。<br />\n我個人認為對症下藥係重要關鍵。<br />\n到底係咩意思呢？<br />\n啫係既然林鄭唔回應，我地就應該針對各項訴求搵返相應嘅部門要求回應。當我地向正確嘅地方表達訴求，軟化嘅市民先會覺得我地嘅抗爭/爭取方式合情合理，先會諒解我地。<br />\n<br />\n我地目的只係想爭取我地覺得值得或者係我地應該要爭取嘅野。<br />\n1) 「撤回」修訂逃犯條例草案<br />\n2)  撤銷示威者「暴動罪」控罪<br />\n3) 「追究」警隊濫用暴力以及權力<br />\n4)  全面收回612「暴動」定義<br />\n<br />\n所以話6月21號。<br />\n我地嘅戰場唔再單單係立會，可以係其他地方。<br />\n用物理上阻撓嘅人可以選擇政總/警總/禮賓府等地表達自己嘅訴求。<br />\n<br />\n但係係咪啫係話21號之前我地咩都做唔到？<br />\n唔係！<br />\n文宣嘅野要提前做，而且要做足。<br />\n例如幾點會行動升級，點樣去升級，我地嘅訴求係D咩。最重要嘅係林鄭點樣無視我地嘅訴求，而導致我地要升級行動。<br />\n而平日好多時間嘅人我建議你地善用下監警會嘅制度，使用方法如下︰<br />\n-&gt;打開香港警務處嘅網站<br />\n-&gt;揀選電子報案中心<br />\n-&gt;選擇其他在線服務<br />\n-&gt;進入投訴警察界面<br />\n-&gt;中間位置會有5個選項，選擇最底「網上報案表格 &ndash; 投訴警察」<br />\n<br />\n緊記要係啱嘅地方做啱嘅野！<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想繼續行動升級，除左武力攻入政府，外國嘅實例有好多都有參考價值。<br />\n只要我地抗爭嘅行為可以做到損害政府利益，而令市民受惠，社會嘅反彈就會少好多。<br />\n我冇煽動大家去咁做，但係我地一齊回顧下以前革命嘅案例<br />\n<br />\n捷克斯洛伐克嘅天鵝絨革命(遊行示威)<br />\n成功嘅原因係持之以恆，<br />\n防暴警察在布拉格鎮壓學生示威。該事件引發了從11月19日到12月下旬的一系列示威，真正示威開始到成功用左1個月多嘅時間。<br />\n<br />\n亞美尼亞示威(不合作運動)<br />\n成功嘅原因係團結一致。<br />\n癱瘓交通︰<br />\n1)十幾人至幾十人為單位係城市各處自發堵路，而且在警察執法時大多都會配合離去（但去附近重新堵路）<br />\n2)用合理速度橫過行人優先嘅班馬線，或在守法情況下不斷橫過馬路（係香港，15米內沒有合適過路設施，中間又沒有欄杆路障，就可以直接橫過馬路）。<br />\n3)鐘意踩單車嘅人，都可以係馬路上面合法騎行，只要保持單行（但可以佔據一條行車線保障自己安全），而且入黑後配有頭燈尾燈即可。乘客搭地鐵也有權力及理由在月台靜候舒適和有空位可坐嘅列車。<br />\n<br />\n法國黃背心運動(暴力抗爭)<br />\n成功嘅原因係出其不意<br />\n1)特定時間，不同地點<br />\n佢地逢週六湧上街，地點路線不定，不死守任何公共空間，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，等汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。<br />\n2)以錯誤訊息攻其不備<br />\n係時間上創造優勢，譬如模糊確實嘅行動日期時間，達到攻其不備嘅效果。<br />\n3)靈活運用抗爭者<br />\n突襲佔領重要的權力地標，開放予公眾集會(和理非)，但半夜出其不意棄守陣地，轉戰其他地方，以虛耗防暴警察的資源。<br />\n<br />\n最後今次反送中將會係大家寶貴經驗，因為相信好多人今次係第一次企出黎爭取自己覺得重要嘅野。如果大家嘅目光長遠到雙普選架話，緊記今次嘅經驗，將來出黎要以身作則，傳授比下一次嘅新人。"},{"pid":"ab434a392c46635e1f4cb85f291bcf6ea444bf30","tid":1241002,"uid":117399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae132c8d971a68482ce669e6271ff3d3469ede17","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1289539f908a85a25fdb0a3b4a47d270b4104205","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcbcce44592db485c7fed6ca934accdbd2b00ea3","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06908a213538ebfef59655a60f6d3d614a0363e3","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fec0a9745bf6a88d6aa01751c1d6ad3c34a2a54","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67599c245a16bf37d2b0f1f689a66127d54bd8a6","tid":1241002,"uid":156611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f36ca45dcde5dc8be41d2f863a94e7a23c6992","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b32321cd80f20a00b24fb953c6541d7051fa2841","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2736bb595b8a5b85023fb9e65add340b4d662b60","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1124ba0041b690327254b98718665764263a7f4","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8475c112946e8c00e11fe6cf7f8d671428cfe854","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:30:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"928a3780aacbf0d53511993ba3168ab0e5fabe73","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f86952c16e4f4d78112f03bdb747754ac86c2b33","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ee1b5846c44ed47a0a2703fb35d5f5553800ea4","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf0dac4a7871b50c7cfe2b37a40032aa97a0a2af","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d03b8530ef4fab574a4e76b268e378c8e1f18982","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:36:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b39a98de5f914d04d24f64a5399d35002640d75","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f391d7c3a8eae6c55bb1ac88b179605883dd5286","tid":1241002,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"適當嘅聚集同休息好重要,保持住度氣"},{"pid":"bbcce8cf4c387f7ecbc94b3b90fda51985875702","tid":1241002,"uid":54381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8240e318fcf2cafb4791786057427995019bedb4","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33bad35daa5e8443401762c1d7b973f6f38b9658","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78594ced27cafff69fa764cd65c740dd91707333","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d7c4650467e58ae0292d4886d40518d412aee82","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d701489d2e8880f4461071ec46aba25654a8db","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad710e5e9e1419f09a99a125e180550cf70c313","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06353482849e93bc32e36b38b5fd940b94dc8753","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7e1957cf90f215f2cba9b3eb7543577eb3848b3","tid":1241002,"uid":61830,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n今次靠我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大部份人已經軟化緊<br />\n係睇我地仲可以作戰幾耐"},{"pid":"aa0dcfb7bc648d3e1e50a8b238e51eb6128a2017","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b1b6853f1322b75d4edd649318387f072222824","tid":1241002,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4a0a40cf530ea3db8b45493d5eb58c65333dfb4","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"民意好重要！<br />\n民意好重要！<br />\n民意好重要！<br />\n我有一個前提想睇大家係咪同意嘅<br />\n大家覺唔覺得林鄭道完歉之後，市民有軟化跡象？<br />\n雖然話遊行人數達到約200萬人，但係都有人係因為烈士而出黎，所以未必反映到不滿林鄭唔直接回應訴求嘅真實數字。<br />\n其實好大機會下次遊行人數就會開始下跌。<br />\n當軟化嘅市民見到政府有所謂嘅讓步，而我地依然咁激進架話，佢地可能會覺得我地唔理智，甚至係無理取鬧。<br />\n咁點樣先可以令我地嘅行為合理化呢？<br />\n我地要合理化到，即使軟化咗嘅市民都唔會有太大抗拒感。<br />\n我個人認為對症下藥係重要關鍵。<br />\n到底係咩意思呢？<br />\n啫係既然林鄭唔回應，我地就應該針對各項訴求搵返相應嘅部門要求回應。當我地向正確嘅地方表達訴求，軟化嘅市民先會覺得我地嘅抗爭/爭取方式合情合理，先會諒解我地。<br />\n<br />\n我地目的只係想爭取我地覺得值得或者係我地應該要爭取嘅野。<br />\n1) 「撤回」修訂逃犯條例草案<br />\n2)  撤銷示威者「暴動罪」控罪<br />\n3) 「追究」警隊濫用暴力以及權力<br />\n4)  全面收回612「暴動」定義<br />\n<br />\n所以話6月21號。<br />\n我地嘅戰場唔再單單係立會，可以係其他地方。<br />\n用物理上阻撓嘅人可以選擇政總/警總/禮賓府等地表達自己嘅訴求。<br />\n<br />\n但係係咪啫係話21號之前我地咩都做唔到？<br />\n唔係！<br />\n文宣嘅野要提前做，而且要做足。<br />\n例如幾點會行動升級，點樣去升級，我地嘅訴求係D咩。最重要嘅係林鄭點樣無視我地嘅訴求，而導致我地要升級行動。<br />\n而平日好多時間嘅人我建議你地善用下監警會嘅制度，使用方法如下︰<br />\n-&gt;打開香港警務處嘅網站<br />\n-&gt;揀選電子報案中心<br />\n-&gt;選擇其他在線服務<br />\n-&gt;進入投訴警察界面<br />\n-&gt;中間位置會有5個選項，選擇最底「網上報案表格 &ndash; 投訴警察」<br />\n<br />\n緊記要係啱嘅地方做啱嘅野！<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想繼續行動升級，除左武力攻入政府，外國嘅實例有好多都有參考價值。<br />\n只要我地抗爭嘅行為可以做到損害政府利益，而令市民受惠，社會嘅反彈就會少好多。<br />\n我冇煽動大家去咁做，但係我地一齊回顧下以前革命嘅案例<br />\n<br />\n捷克斯洛伐克嘅天鵝絨革命(遊行示威)<br />\n成功嘅原因係持之以恆，<br />\n防暴警察在布拉格鎮壓學生示威。該事件引發了從11月19日到12月下旬的一系列示威，真正示威開始到成功用左1個月多嘅時間。<br />\n<br />\n亞美尼亞示威(不合作運動)<br />\n成功嘅原因係團結一致。<br />\n癱瘓交通︰<br />\n1)十幾人至幾十人為單位係城市各處自發堵路，而且在警察執法時大多都會配合離去（但去附近重新堵路）<br />\n2)用合理速度橫過行人優先嘅班馬線，或在守法情況下不斷橫過馬路（係香港，15米內沒有合適過路設施，中間又沒有欄杆路障，就可以直接橫過馬路）。<br />\n3)鐘意踩單車嘅人，都可以係馬路上面合法騎行，只要保持單行（但可以佔據一條行車線保障自己安全），而且入黑後配有頭燈尾燈即可。乘客搭地鐵也有權力及理由在月台靜候舒適和有空位可坐嘅列車。<br />\n<br />\n法國黃背心運動(暴力抗爭)<br />\n成功嘅原因係出其不意<br />\n1)特定時間，不同地點<br />\n佢地逢週六湧上街，地點路線不定，不死守任何公共空間，不預先公佈時間下快閃式堵路。譬如堵塞高速公路和迴旋處，接管或燒毀道路收費站，等汽車自由通行，令政府無利可圖。<br />\n2)以錯誤訊息攻其不備<br />\n係時間上創造優勢，譬如模糊確實嘅行動日期時間，達到攻其不備嘅效果。<br />\n3)靈活運用抗爭者<br />\n突襲佔領重要的權力地標，開放予公眾集會(和理非)，但半夜出其不意棄守陣地，轉戰其他地方，以虛耗防暴警察的資源。<br />\n<br />\n最後今次反送中將會係大家寶貴經驗，因為相信好多人今次係第一次企出黎爭取自己覺得重要嘅野。如果大家嘅目光長遠到雙普選架話，緊記今次嘅經驗，將來出黎要以身作則，傳授比下一次嘅新人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"可以集中多d 係控告黑警方面，因為好多人仍然對佢地當日行為好唔滿意"},{"pid":"32d0d66919fd21aa4bda7f8db9bcf48ac37aad16","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75c04fc74d300ca1c28f3227bd7b482fd6a14e56","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b6df1839e77a21d57c1d47d8d270d13368657e","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c60d202f2f30309e2e4e1be84dc4e2fd5310a82d","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8a3bf6ee331654a6a99c759b56889076487eaf2","tid":1241002,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4fe03b2f1d7f945291b67bc14edbe1ea74a2c25","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3742a16b8ef451c83a4e62fd4efd1014e5113658","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8a68745ae5ad22002d962c330f9d39f57648c70","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26cff5d0035eec4f2c3efd49c3da17f97cd8fbbf","tid":1241002,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"上禮拜夠話跌<br />\n點知100變200"},{"pid":"e9e96c7b4bf06efc734f583b7c8db3feef97517d","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c052b50411c344fad8c667ea7c018c4f36d36f42","tid":1241002,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01ee3e97900847d408cbee1f6f84f5897a7c4422","tid":1241002,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"81e8e704fd995e651c705c5beff4b3